---
---

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="newsletter-preview fade-in">
    <div class="newsletter-left">
      <div class="section-label">// The newsletter feature</div>
      <h2>YOUR REVIEWS.<br />A WEEKLY<br />NEWSLETTER.</h2>
      <p>Every week MemeMyReviews writes and sends you a fully formatted newsletter built around your best reviews — with the meme pack already inside.</p>
      <ul class="nl-bullets">
        <li>Top 5 funniest reviews of the week, turned into memes</li>
        <li>Pre-written intro and CTA copy — just add your logo</li>
        <li>Ready to send via Mailchimp, Klaviyo, or Beehiiv</li>
        <li>Lands in your inbox every Monday at 9am</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="newsletter-right">
      <div class="newsletter-card">
        <div class="nl-card-header">
          <div class="nl-card-header-left">
            <div class="nl-logo-sm">Meme<span>My</span>Reviews</div>
          </div>
          <span class="nl-date">MON, JAN 6 &middot; ISSUE #14</span>
        </div>
        <div class="nl-card-body">
          <div class="nl-subject">This Week's Reviews Were Actually Unhinged &#x1f525;</div>
          <div class="nl-meta">From: MemeMyReviews Weekly &middot; To: Your Subscribers</div>
          <div class="nl-section-label">&#x1f3ad; This Week's Meme Pack</div>
          <div class="nl-meme-row">
            <div class="nl-meme-thumb">WHEN YOUR PRODUCT HITS DIFFERENT</div>
            <div class="nl-meme-thumb t2">MY HUSBAND DIDN'T BELIEVE ME</div>
            <div class="nl-meme-thumb t3">5 STARS. WOULD OBSESS AGAIN.</div>
          </div>
          <hr class="nl-divider" />
          <div class="nl-section-label">&#x1f4dd; Editor's Note</div>
          <div class="nl-copy">Your customers are out here writing comedy gold in the review section and nobody's using it. This week's batch had us crying. Enjoy the memes — share them everywhere.</div>
          <a href="#" class="nl-cta">View Full Newsletter &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .newsletter-preview {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .newsletter-preview {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 64px;
    }
  }

  .newsletter-left p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 440px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .newsletter-left p {
      font-size: 17px;
    }
  }

  .newsletter-left h2 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .nl-bullets {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 28px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .nl-bullets li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .nl-bullets li::before {
    content: '\2192';
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .newsletter-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px var(--black);
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .newsletter-card {
      max-width: none;
    }
  }

  .nl-card-header {
    background: var(--black);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .nl-card-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
    }
  }

  .nl-card-header-left {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .nl-logo-sm {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .nl-logo-sm span {
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .nl-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #666;
  }

  .nl-card-body {
    padding: 20px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .nl-card-body {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }

  .nl-subject {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .nl-subject {
      font-size: 22px;
    }
  }

  .nl-meta {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .nl-section-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .nl-meme-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .nl-meme-row {
      gap: 10px;
    }
  }

  .nl-meme-thumb {
    flex: 1;
    height: 70px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f0e8, #e8e0d5);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .nl-meme-thumb {
      height: 80px;
      font-size: 10px;
      padding: 8px;
    }
  }

  .nl-meme-thumb.t2 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff0ea, #ffe5d5);
  }

  .nl-meme-thumb.t3 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffde7, #fff8cc);
  }

  .nl-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  .nl-copy {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .nl-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 16px;
    background: var(--orange);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  .nl-cta:hover {
    color: var(--white);
    background: var(--orange-hover);
  }
</style>
